---

<BaseLayout
  title="Beauty & Aesthetics Marketing Singapore | Jraft Creative"
  description="Digital marketing for beauty salons, hair salons, nail studios, spas, and aesthetics clinics in Singapore. Website design, SEO, social media, and paid ads tailored to the beauty industry."
  canonical="https://jraftcreative.com/industries/beauty-aesthetics/"
  currentPath="/industries/beauty-aesthetics/"
  schema={schemaData}
>
  <section class="service-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <ol>
          <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="/industries/">Industries</a></li>
          <li aria-current="page">Beauty &amp; Aesthetics</li>
        </ol>
      </nav>
      <div class="service-hero-content reveal">
        <h1>Beauty &amp; Aesthetics Marketing</h1>
        <p class="service-hero-sub">The beauty industry in Singapore is competitive and highly visual. We help salons, spas, and aesthetics clinics grow online — through websites built for bookings, SEO that targets high-intent searches, and social media content that converts browsers into clients.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <h2>Beauty &amp; Aesthetics Businesses We Work With</h2>
        <p>Select your business type to see the specific services available for your industry.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="industry-detail-grid" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
        {subIndustries.map((sub, i) => (
          <div class={`industry-detail-card reveal${i > 0 ? ` reveal-d${Math.min(i, 4)}` : ''}`}>
            <h3><a href={sub.href}>{sub.name}</a></h3>
            <p>{sub.description}</p>
            <div class="industry-detail-services">
              {sub.services.map(service => (
                <a href={service.href}>{service.label}</a>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <h2>Why Beauty Businesses Need Specialised Marketing</h2>
        <p>Generic digital marketing does not work for beauty and aesthetics. The sector has unique demands — from visually driven discovery on Instagram to the need for seamless online booking integration — that require a focused approach.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="features-grid" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
        <div class="feature-card reveal">
          <h3>Online Booking Integration</h3>
          <p>We build websites that connect directly with booking platforms such as Fresha and Booksy, so clients can schedule appointments without calling or messaging on WhatsApp.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card reveal reveal-d1">
          <h3>Before &amp; After Galleries</h3>
          <p>Visual proof is the most effective conversion tool in beauty. We design gallery sections that showcase your work and give prospective clients confidence to book.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card reveal reveal-d2">
          <h3>Instagram &amp; Social Presence</h3>
          <p>Beauty is one of the most searched categories on Instagram in Singapore. We manage content strategies that build following, drive saves, and translate engagement into bookings.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card reveal reveal-d3">
          <h3>Treatment Menus &amp; Pricing Pages</h3>
          <p>Clearly structured treatment menus reduce friction and improve search visibility. We write and optimise service pages that rank for the specific treatments your clients are searching for.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="text-align: center;">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <h2>Ready to Grow Your Beauty Business?</h2>
        <p>Get a free consultation and a tailored marketing plan for your salon, spa, or aesthetics clinic.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal reveal-d1">
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 1rem;">Get a Free Quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
